{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_totter_set_2", "eventName": "歸鄉", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "歸鄉", "storyInfo": "鉛踝回到自己的家鄉，想要找尋一處安靜的居所休息，度過最後的時光，但陰差陽錯下，他的平靜日子一去不返。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切都始自公司的廁所，那天我在馬桶上嚎啕大哭，為自己一團亂的人生感到絕望。"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隔間外，幾位剛從薩爾貢度假回來的同事聊起了自己的假日時光，從他們口中我聽到了一個名字，與一段讓我平靜下來的妙論。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，我背起行囊，歷盡艱辛，從哥倫比亞的鋼鐵叢林到薩爾貢的茂密雨林，最終抵達此地，見到了那位智者。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_jungle_1", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎來到靜修之地，怎麼樣，你今天見到智者了嗎？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常榮幸，雖然見到智者時已經很晚了，但他還是耐心傾聽了我的問題，並為我解答。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他怎麼說？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他用行動代替了言語，默默地捲著自己手上的繩索。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……繩索？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，智者是想告訴我，煩惱如亂麻，但只要耐心以對，就能將其編織為一根根繩索。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後它們自然就會柔順地盤繞在手心，不再讓人頭痛。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳……有道理，很有道理，不愧是智者。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，你的悟性也很高，能夠迅速領悟智者言行舉止間所蘊含的真理。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，分別時，智者還滿含深意地看了我一眼，我想，這正是他對我的讚許吧。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，你說得對……", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，一開始，我還以為這次的心靈之旅只是傳得誇張。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們跟從智者指引，從不會欺騙他人。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，我今天會帶著滿足睡去。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就祝你有個好夢吧，先生。明天的講座將在早上八點準時開始，屆時將由我帶領大家前往會場。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_falls_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……人們獨自走過自己的一生……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猶如泛孤舟於湖面……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瀑布下，智者盤坐在湖中央的巨石上，為湖邊眾人講述著他從潺潺流水中獲得的哲思，語調和緩。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾人凝神，感受著溫和的話語如同流水般浸潤內心。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，朋友，你來多久了？", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天才來，你呢？來多久了？", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經快一個月了，想不到吧，一個月前我還沉浸在上一段感情的陰影中，頹廢異常。", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是你現在看著容光煥發……哦，肯定是智者。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，是他帶領我走出了悲痛。", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到人群中的談論，智者停頓片刻，看向遠方，向眾人展露笑容。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，智者往我這邊看了！我……", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦……智者的眼睛是多麼溫柔，好像能療癒我內心的苦悶。", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感覺……在他那迷離的、充滿仁愛與理解的目光中，我將與周遭萬物達成和解。", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要意識到發生在我們身上的種種就像我們身邊的流水……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……終究只是匆匆而過，不會停留。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！是那個動作，智者的招牌動作，他向眾人伸出了手！", "name": "玻利瓦爾旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦！他要說出那句話了！", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是什麼？！智者要說什麼？！", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_065", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別急！他馬上就會講了！", "name": "萊塔尼亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_065"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下對生活的期待……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_065"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任流水帶我去遠方！", "name": "各國旅人"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇哦。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_falls_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "托特爾，你中間停了一下，為什麼？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到人群中有聲音，所以停下來看看。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，是哪個傢伙不專心？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，沒戴眼鏡看不清楚。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……下次講座可以換個地方嗎？水邊蚊子太多了。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，也沒下次了，按照我們的劇本，你馬上就要退居幕後了。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……總算要結束了。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧你，我們這幾個月靠遊客賺了不少錢。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，要不是這幾年過得實在太潦倒，我們也不至於為難你一個病患。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，離開家鄉這麼久，兩手空空地回來，說實在真有些對不起大家……能幫著大家找到一個發財之路也蠻好。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟父親離開後，是鄉親們為我湊齊路費，如今也該換我報答大家。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來也真是不好意思，打擾了你最後的平靜生活。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也沒有預料到順手救下那個旅遊團會帶來這麼多麻煩。誰知道他們回去後亂講了什麼，突然某天就有一堆人找上門來……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，乍聽之下還以為是村子裡出了個大人物。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順著他們的話說了一陣子後，才明白他們找的人是你，本來還打算繼續編些故事從他們手裡賺點情報費的。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你這個騙錢的計劃從那時就有雛形了嗎？", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是講了他們想聽的話而已，順著別人心意講話可是要技巧的，收點錢又怎麼了？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（瞇眼）", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，比起移動城市的心理諮詢師，確實也沒收多少。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你的報酬為什麼要退回來，那可是很大一筆錢，你就沒有什麼想要的東西了嗎？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒……我只想平靜地度過接下來的日子。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你像河水般接納投入其中的所有事物，自會流向遠方。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這不是明天劇本裡的台詞嗎？", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，看來你已經看過劇本了。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我與智者同行的時間是如此短暫。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在雨林裡停留半個月後，他突然向所有人宣布，要離開大家，開始一段新的旅程，去往一個全新的地方。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他宣布了自己的死訊。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_falls_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，這是有什麼急事嗎？", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也並不知情，智者只是讓我通知大家聚集在這裡。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，您不早點告訴我，我還穿著自己的睡衣呢……這樣衣衫不整去見智者多冒犯。", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨無妨，智者本人不拘小節，不會在意這些的。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，看……", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茂密的雨林中，幾隻角獸緩緩走出，在瀑布邊駐足。片刻後，又有更多動物走出雨林，聚在岸邊。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一條鱗躍出水面，激起的水紋卻久久不散。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨即，眾人發現，河水早已靜止，甚至從懸崖傾瀉而下的水簾也不再流動。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而智者從水簾後緩緩走出，身著素衣。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位，久等了。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音剛落，河水再次流動。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者！！", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎哎，你別一直往前擠啊！！", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次我一定要靠近一點，讓智者看到我支持他的模樣！", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者，天才剛亮，您要和我們講什麼？", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天晚上，我在叢林夜遊的時候，看到星光從樹葉的間隙灑下，落在湖面上，我……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……諸位……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡我看到了自己生命的盡頭……呼喚你們來到這裡，只是想與大家告別。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是在開玩笑嗎，智者？", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒謬至極，智者從來不開玩笑。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者，難道您能預知自己的未來嗎？", "name": "玻利瓦爾旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未來與過去不過是一條河流的兩段，只要身處河水中，自然就能從水面蕩起的波紋中解讀出遠方傳來的訊息。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但窺見自己的命運是要付出代價的，我感覺到自己正在被此地排斥，在這世間的旅途也即將走到盡頭。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者……面對死亡，您為何這樣無動於衷？", "name": "維多利亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在離開前，我早已接受自己的結局，尋覓到了內心的平靜。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位也不要為我傷心，死亡對我來說，不過是另一段旅程，另一段修行。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，您的面龐，看起來是多麼寧靜……", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早已對歷經的一切釋懷，正如河水接納投入其中的所有事物，然後兀自流向遠方。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_201", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者，在您離開前，可否告訴我您是如何解讀這一切的？！", "name": "玻利瓦爾旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天機不可洩露。", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別了，諸位……", "name": "“智者”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_aerialview", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻羽獸落在智者的肩膀，他閉上雙眼，垂下頭，好似進入深眠。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他腳下，河水急速流動，形成漩渦。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "水花高高濺起，再一眨眼，智者便沉入漩渦中心了。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只留下一個小小漩渦，在湖面靜靜旋轉。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在哥倫比亞，我是個失敗的傢伙，不僅破產，家庭也瀕臨破碎，但此次旅行令我找回了重新面對生活的勇氣。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者面對死亡時的豁達與超脫令我深信，總會有一條河流帶走我曾經的傷痛。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_jungle_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$leaveshake", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪……這好像不是約定好的地方。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那傢伙是怎麼挖水道的？真是的，竟然拐到這裡來了。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者？", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "河水緩緩流過，正如時光在……", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都懂的，您不必說了。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會說出去嗎？", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道嗎？我的真實身分其實是僱傭兵。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……放心好了，要說的話我早就說了。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從第一天來到這裡後，我就察覺到不對了，那些淺顯的大道理其實很難打動誰。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你們看起來並無異議。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……為什麼要有？", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡風景不錯，吃得很好，扮演智者的人也很好看——就是老兄你啦。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更重要的是，這裡花費不高，大家都覺得來度假很划算。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我每次表演，你們都很投入，就像是對此深信不疑。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好吧，我一直把它當作景點特色體驗來玩的，之前在龍門我也玩過，不過那時扮演的角色是黑幫小弟。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒有去過龍門。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以去看看，蠻好玩的。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想應該沒有什麼機會了。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心好了，都是看破不說破。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家來到這裡稍微喘口氣，短暫地逃避現實生活中的煩惱，誰會在乎是真是假。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正最後我們都要回到那條屬於我們自己的河流。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像智者說的。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，就像智者說的，我們的煩惱在那裡，我們的牽掛也在那裡。", "name": "哥倫比亞旅人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "托特爾，其實……如果你想留在辦事處也可以，羅德島有非常完備的臨終關懷計劃。", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很感激，但我還是想在家鄉度過人生最後的時光。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你不是說聯絡不到在家鄉的家人嗎？", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，因為他們都過世了。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你回去豈不是要孤身一人……", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那很好。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哪裡好了。", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人很安靜。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身邊人的憐憫和悲傷會讓我感到煩惱。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_village", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿去，乾衣服，趕快換上。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼現在才過來？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們找不到其他辦法了嗎？從瀑布游到這裡並不近。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一個方案是讓你隨著紛飛的羽獸一起消失，不過有個缺點，就是會全身沾滿羽獸糞便。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那算了，還不如這個。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我離開後，這場謝幕仍能一直為這裡吸引源源不斷的旅客。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實……雨林這麼大，我們絕對能找到一處平靜的居所供你休息，你沒必要離開的。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我保證，來往的旅客不會打擾到你安寧自在的日子，至於衣食住行的花費，大家來出，你需要什麼說一聲就是了。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，我還是打算離開。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許在大家眼裡我是個油嘴滑舌的傢伙，但你和我一起長大，我不會騙你。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，知道，我又不傻。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那為什麼？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者說的是對的，我應當去尋找一條真正能夠接納我，且使我感到平靜的河流。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者不就是你自己？", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是，我只是扮演他的人。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_070", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，他說的話可都是我亂寫的，托特爾。", "name": "智者侍從"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無所謂，反正我過日子也是隨便亂來的。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "智者是否真實存在並不重要，但有一件事是肯定的。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們總是會有煩惱與牽絆，只有接受這一切，才能讓人真正平靜。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想我已經準備好重新面對未來了。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算算時間……托特爾回家鄉已經半年多了，再過半年，我們一起找個時間去看看他吧。", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_088", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "羅德島信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_088"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨……那個……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "托特爾？！", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……出了一些事情，原定計劃改變了。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之我回來了……", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你現在……打算是……不是……我腦袋有點亂。", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_088", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，既然你回來了，那我就沒必要去雨林裡找你了，之前有封你的信寄到這裡來了。", "name": "羅德島信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_088"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……給我的？", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_088"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從哪裡寄來的？", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_088"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_088", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雪原。", "name": "羅德島信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_088"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪……", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_012", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰寄來的？", "name": "羅德島外勤幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "middle", "name": "avg_4062_totter_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……我想，應該是一些以前的朋友。", "name": "托特爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}